From: David Brownell <>
Subject: Re: [PATCH 10/13, revised] drivers/usb/gadget: use USB API functions rather than constants
Sender: linux-kernel-owner@vger.kernel.org
Precedence: bulk
List-ID: <linux-kernel.vger.kernel.org>
